CTRL + N            =>  Treeview in NVChad
CTRL + W + W        =>  Toggle between Treeview and Active file
CTRL + L            =>  Focus Rechts Fenster
CTRL + H            =>  Focus left Window
gt / :tabn          =>  next tab
gT / :tabp          =>  previous tab
:tabnew             =>  new tab
TAB (KEY)           =>  toggle between tabs
:q                  =>  close tab
SPACE -> F -> M     =>  Format Code.
SPACE -> H          =>  Toggle Terminal
CTRL + X            =>  Back to Normal mode (ex. from Terminal)
